content.rendered:
Directed by Nila Madhab Panda.

Written by Nitin Dixit.

Cast Sanjay Mishra(Hedu). Ranvir Shorey(Gunu Babu). Tillotama Shome(Parvati). Bhupesh Singh(Mukund). Ekta Sawant(Kuhu). Tanya Sejwal(Pihu).Ramesh Kumar Chaudhary. Praveen Kondaparthi(Prakash).Amit Singh. Shrikant Verma(School teacher)

Language Hindi.

Producers Kapil Madnani. Manish Mundra. Nila Madhab Panda. Akshay Kumar Parija. Supratik Roy. Vasu Sharma. Kapil Tanwar. Anuj Tyagi.

Production Akshay Parija Production. Drishyam Film. Eleanora Images Private Limite.
